(416, 'Baby Animals Crossword Puzzle', 'Click on each box to type letters into the crossword puzzle. (use this as a follow up activity after studying baby animals)', 'http://iteslj.org/cw/2/em-babyanimal.html', '', 'Life Science-Young to Adults', '3,k', '', 'Interactive', '2015-04-22 17:49:42'),
