(427, 'Dress a Bear for the Weather', 'careful, he''s fussy! (this activity asks students to make a judgment about weather based on a thermometer) this also works well for math', 'http://www.fossweb.com/modulesK-2/AirandWeather/activities/whatstheweather.html', '', 'Earth Science-Weather Data', 'k', '', 'Interactive', '2015-04-22 17:49:43'),
