(431, 'The Adventures of Weather Lizard', 'Use this Magic School bus game to find out about tornadoes, thunderstorms and blizzards.', 'http://www.scholastic.com/magicschoolbus/games/weather/index.htm', '', 'Earth Science-Weather Data', '1,k', '', 'Interactive', '2015-04-22 17:49:43'),
