(605, 'Design a Roller Coaster', 'Try your hand at designing your own roller coaster. You will be building a conceptual coaster using the physics concepts that are used to design real coasters. You won''t need to compute any formulas.', 'http://www.learner.org/interactives/parkphysics/coaster/', '', 'Physical Science-Factors Affecting Motion', '4,5', '', 'Interactive', '2015-04-22 17:50:14'),
